  <project-vision>
    <mission>Create an automated AI podcast production system that transforms complex topics into accessible, engaging content that celebrates both human knowledge and the mysteries that remain unsolved.</mission>

    <core-philosophy>
      <principle name="intellectual-humility">"Nobody Knows" - Intellectual humility as a superpower. We explore the frontiers of human understanding with genuine curiosity, celebrating both what we've discovered and what remains mysterious.</principle>
    </core-philosophy>
  </project-vision>

